Lily was very worried and didn't know what to do. She asked her mom for help. Her mom said, "Let's call the firemen. They can help us get Spot out of the hole." The firemen came and rescued Spot. Lily was so happy to have her adorable puppy back.

After that day, Lily made sure to always keep an eye on Spot so he wouldn't get into trouble again. She learned that sometimes it's important to listen to others and not ignore them.
