Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Timmy. Timmy loved to eat pears, they were his favorite fruit. One day, Timmy went to the store with his mommy to buy some pears. When they got home, Timmy accidentally dropped a pear and it broke into pieces. Timmy was sad because he couldn't eat the pear anymore. 

But then, Timmy had an idea. He decided to be brave and try to fix the pear. He used glue to put the pieces back together, but it didn't work. Timmy was disappointed. Suddenly, Timmy's little sister came in and accidentally stepped on the pear, destroying it completely. Timmy was sad at first, but then he realized it was okay because he still had more pears to eat.
<|end|>


