Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She lived in a small town with her mommy and daddy. One day, Lily and her mommy went to the park to play. It was a messy day because it rained a lot.

Lily saw her friend Tommy at the park. "Hi Tommy!" said Lily. "Do you want to play with me?"

Tommy nodded his head and said, "Yes, I do!"

Lily and Tommy played on the swings and the slide. They had so much fun together. After they finished playing, Lily's mommy said, "It's time to go home now."

Lily said goodbye to Tommy and they both nodded their heads. They walked home and talked about their fun day at the park. When they got home, Lily's mommy gave her a bath to wash away the mess from the rainy day. Lily was tired and went to bed with a smile on her face, dreaming about her next playdate with Tommy.
