Once upon a time, there was a planet called Earth. Many animals lived on Earth, like cats, dogs, and birds. One day, a poor little bird was flying in the sky when it saw a big scary hawk. The hawk wanted to eat the bird, but the bird was too small and weak to protect itself.

The bird saw a cat on the ground and flew down to talk to it. "Please help me, Mr. Cat! There's a mean hawk trying to eat me!" said the bird. The cat replied, "Don't worry, little bird. I will protect you."

The cat chased the hawk away and saved the poor little bird. From that day on, the bird and the cat became good friends and protected each other from any danger they faced. They knew that protecting each other was important, just like protecting our planet Earth.
