"That's a university, Timmy," his mom replied.

"What's a university?" Timmy asked.

"It's a place where grown-ups go to learn new things and become really smart," his mom explained.

Timmy thought for a moment and then said, "I want to go to university one day and become really clever too." His mom smiled and said, "I know you will, Timmy." Then, Timmy saw a bug and poked it with his finger. "Look, Mommy, I poked it!" he said excitedly.
