Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to play with her blocks. She had a lot of blocks that she could build big towers with.

One day, Lily's friend came over to play. Her friend was a bit bossy and wanted to build the tower all by herself. Lily didn't like that. She wanted to have fun playing together.

So, Lily told her friend that they could build the tower together. They both had a lot of blocks and they built the biggest tower they had ever seen. They were so happy that they played together all day long. From that day on, they always shared their blocks and had fun together.
<|end|>


