Once upon a time, there was a boy named Timmy. Timmy had a very hairy dog named Max. Max liked to play fetch with Timmy. One day, while playing fetch, Max accidentally hit Timmy's nose with the ball. Timmy's nose hurt a lot, so he went home to tell his mom.

His mom looked at his nose and saw that it was red. She gave him a tissue to wipe his nose and told him to rest. After a while, Timmy's nose stopped hurting and he felt better. He decided to return to the park to play with Max again. When he got there, Max was waiting for him with the ball in his mouth. Timmy was happy to see his furry friend and they continued playing fetch together.
<|end|>


