Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to play with her colorful cube toys. Every day, she would spend hours building towers and castles with them. 

One day, Lily's grandma came to visit. She brought a big bag of cookies and they had a tea party together. Lily was very happy to have her grandma visit. 

After they finished their tea and cookies, Lily's grandma helped her organize her cube toys. They put them all in a neat pile and it made Lily very happy. She loved how organized they looked. 

From that day on, Lily made sure to keep her cube toys organized so that she could show her grandma when she visited again.
