Once upon a time, there was a big earthquake. The ground shook and things fell down. People were scared and ran outside to be safe. A little dog named Max ran away from his home during the earthquake. His owner, a little girl named Lily, was sad and worried. She looked for Max everywhere but couldn't find him. 

Days passed and Lily didn't give up. She put up posters and asked everyone she saw if they had seen Max. One day, a kind man found Max and brought him back to Lily. Max was happy to be home and licked Lily's face. Lily forgave Max for running away because she was just happy to have him back. Max was a loyal dog and never ran away again.
<|end|>


