Once upon a time, there was a dog named Max. Max loved to stand in the sun and feel the warm rays on his fur. One day, Max's owner gave him a treat. It was a bone that Max loved to chew. Max was so happy and he felt fine.

Max went outside to play with his friends. They ran and played together, but Max wanted to show off his new treat. He stood up on his hind legs and held the bone in his mouth. His friends were impressed and wanted to play with Max's bone. Max was happy to share his treat and they all had a fine time together.
