Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to play outside in the big green field behind her house. One day, she saw a butterfly with wild colors on its wings. It was so pretty and she wanted to bring it closer to her. 

Lily ran back to her house to get a jar. She carefully caught the butterfly and brought it back to her room. She wanted to show her mom the wild butterfly, but she realized she was still wearing her pajamas. 

Lily quickly put on her favorite dress, the one with the pink flowers on it. She showed her mom the butterfly and they both admired its wild colors. Lily was so happy that she could bring the butterfly inside to show her mom.
