Once upon a time, there was a curious little girl named Amy. She loved to play in the kitchen with her mom. One day, Amy saw a big, round peach on the table. She asked her mom, "What can we make with this peach?"

Her mom said, "Let's mix the peach with some other fruits to make a yummy fruit salad!" They cut the peach into small pieces and mixed it with other fruits like apples, bananas, and grapes.

Amy shared the fruit salad with her friends. They all loved it! After they finished eating, Amy's mom told them, "When we mix different things together, we can create something new and wonderful. Just like the fruit salad, we can learn from each other and become better friends."

The kids learned that being curious and trying new things can bring happiness and make the world a better place. And they all lived happily ever after.
