Lily wanted to help the little star. She had an idea! She told the star, "I will find a new light for you to replace your old one. Then you will be the perfect, bright star in the universe!" The little star was so happy and thanked Lily.

Lily searched and searched until she found the perfect light for the little star. She gave it to the star, and it replaced its old light with the new one. Now the little star was the brightest star in the universe, and it was all thanks to Lily. They both were very happy and became best friends forever.
