One sunny day, Tom and Max went to the park. They saw a big tree with gum on it. Tom wanted to use his paws to get the gum, but the tree was too tall. Max had an idea. He told Tom to climb on his back.

Tom climbed on Max's back and reached for the gum. With a big smile, Tom got the gum and shared it with Max. They were so happy. From that day on, Tom and Max always helped each other and had fun together.
