One day, a little boy named Tim went for a walk in nature. He saw many trees, flowers, and animals. He heard a mysterious sound that went "ring, ring, ring." Tim was scared but curious, so he followed the sound.

He found a little bird who was making the sound. The bird said, "I lost my mom! Can you help me find her?" Tim wanted to help, so they went to look for the bird's mom together.

They looked all around, but could not find the mom. Then, they heard another "ring, ring, ring" sound. The little bird became happy and said, "That's my mom!" They followed the sound and found the mom. The two birds were very happy, and Tim felt good for helping his new friends.
