Suddenly, a big dog came running and barked at them. Tim and Sue felt guilty because they thought they did something bad. The old man came and told the dog to stop. He said it was okay, and they didn't do anything wrong. Tim and Sue smiled and thanked the old man. They knew they had to be more careful next time.
