Jane went to the dog and asked, "Can I play with you and your toy?" The dog wagged its tail and barked. Jane knew the dog said yes.

They played together all day. Jane threw the toy and the dog ran to get it. They had a lot of fun. In the end, Jane and the humble dog became good friends.
