Once upon a time, there was a charming little girl named Lily. Lily loved to shine her light on fun things. One day, she found a book with a quiz inside. She was very excited and wanted to share it with her friend, Sam.

Lily ran to Sam's house and said, "Sam, I found a fun quiz! Let's do it together!" Sam smiled and said, "That sounds great, Lily! I love quizzes!" They sat down and began to play with the quiz. They had to find the right words to fill in the blanks. It was a little hard, but they worked together.

As they finished the quiz, the sun began to set. Lily had an idea. She grabbed her flashlight and said, "Sam, let's shine our lights on the quiz and see if we can find more fun things to do!" They shined their lights on the quiz, and a secret message appeared. It said, "You are both smart and kind friends!" Lily and Sam smiled, happy to have spent the day together with their charming quiz.
