Once upon a time, there was a brown dog. The brown dog lived in a small house in the west. He had a lot of friends. They played together every day.

One day, the brown dog found a big crab. The crab was very pinchy. The brown dog wanted to play with the crab, but he was scared of the pinch. He thought of a plan. The brown dog would show the crab to his friends, and they would all play together.

The brown dog took the pinchy crab to his friends. They all wanted to play, but the crab was too pinchy. The crab pinched all the friends one by one. The friends were sad and hurt. They ran away from the brown dog and the pinchy crab.

The brown dog was sad too. He lost all his friends because of the pinchy crab. The brown dog went back to his small house in the west. He was all alone. The end.
