"Go!" shouted Pippin, and they all started to run. The penguins ran and ran, laughing and having fun. In the end, Pippin won the race. All the penguins clapped and cheered for him.

Pippin was very happy. He said, "Thank you, friends. Let's play again tomorrow." The penguins all agreed, and they went home to rest for the next day's fun.
