One day, a prince was walking in the forest. He saw a big house with many flowers. He wanted to see who lived there. He knocked on the door, but no one answered. He opened the door and went inside.

He saw a girl sleeping on a bed. She had long hair and a pretty dress. She looked like a princess. The prince thought she was very beautiful. He wanted to wake her up. He leaned over and kissed her.

The girl opened her eyes and smiled. She was not dead, she was only sleeping. A witch had put a spell on her. She said, "Hello, who are you?"

The prince said, "I am a prince. I saw your house and I wanted to meet you. I am sorry, I did not know you were sleeping."

The girl said, "That's okay. You broke the spell with your kiss. You are very brave and kind. What is your name?"

The prince said, "My name is Leo. What is yours?"

The girl said, "My name is Rose. I am happy to see you. Do you want to stay with me?"

The prince said, "Yes, I do. You are the most wonderful girl I have ever met. Do you want to be my princess?"

The girl said, "Yes, I do. You are the most handsome prince I have ever seen. Do you want to be my prince?"

They hugged and kissed. They were very happy. They had a big surprise. They had found true love.
<|end|>


