<|asst|>
Once upon a time, there was a brown dog named Max. Max loved to play in the pool. One sunny day, he went to the pool with his best friend, a little girl named Lucy.

At the pool, they saw a big cat. The cat wanted to fight with Max. Lucy said, "No, no, cat! We don't fight here. We play and have fun in the pool."

The cat listened and stopped. They all played together in the pool. They splashed water and laughed. In the end, they became good friends and had a great day at the pool. And they never fought again.
<|end|>


