Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Sue. Sue loved to ride her red bike. She rode it up and down the street every day. Sue was always very careful when she rode her bike. She made sure to look both ways and never went too fast.

One day, it started to rain while Sue was riding her bike. The rain came down like a big shower from the sky. Sue didn't want to get wet, so she rode her bike very fast to her house. She was still careful, even though she was going fast.

When Sue got home, her mom helped her dry off from the rain shower. Sue told her mom about her ride in the rain. Her mom was happy that Sue was careful on her bike. They laughed and talked about the fun ride in the rain shower.
<|end|>


