Once upon a time, there was a little dog named Max. Max had a big dream. He wanted to perform in front of all his friends. He practiced every day to get ready for the big show.

One day, Max felt ready to perform. He told all his friends to come and watch him. They all sat down, excited to see Max's show. But when Max started, he got embarrassed. He forgot all the tricks he practiced.

Max's friends saw that he was sad. They came up to him and said, "Don't be embarrassed, Max. We all get scared sometimes. Just keep trying." Max felt better and decided to keep practicing. He knew that one day, he would perform his tricks without feeling embarrassed. And his friends would be there to cheer him on.
<|end|>


