One day, a curious dog named Spot went for a walk. He saw a big tree and thought it would be fun to play near it. As he got closer, he heard a strange sound coming from the tree.

Suddenly, a bird appeared from the tree and said, "Hello, dog! My name is Chirpy. Do you want to play with me?" Spot wagged his tail and barked, "Yes, I want to play!"

They played together all day long, running around the tree and chasing each other. Spot and Chirpy became best friends. At the end of the day, they were both very tired but very happy. They promised to meet again near the big tree and play together every day.
<|end|>


