One day, a happy car named Zoom was driving down the road. Zoom was a special car because he was made of shiny metal. He liked to drive fast and make people smile.

As Zoom was driving, he saw a little girl named Lily sitting by the road. She looked sad. Zoom stopped and said, "Hi, I'm Zoom. Why are you sad?"

Lily looked up and said, "I lost my toy. Can you help me find it?" Zoom smiled and said, "Of course! Let's go find your toy together!"

They drove around until they found the toy under a tree. Lily was so happy and said, "Thank you, Zoom!" Zoom was happy too because he made a new friend. From that day on, Zoom and Lily had many fun adventures together.
<|end|>


