One day, a little dog named Max found a big steel pot. The pot was shiny and strong. Max thought it would be fun to perform a show for his friends with the steel pot. He felt comfortable and happy with his idea.

Max called his best friend, a cat named Luna. "Luna, come see my show!" he said. Luna came running to see what Max was doing. She saw the steel pot and smiled. "What a great idea, Max!" she said.

Max put the steel pot on his head like a hat and started to dance. Luna clapped her paws and laughed. All their friends came to watch Max perform with the steel pot. They all had a fun time, and Max felt very proud of his show.
<|end|>


