Once upon a time, there was a green piano in the park. It was a very pretty piano. Many kids loved to play with it.

One day, a little girl named Lily went to the park with her mom. She saw the green piano and said, "Mom, look! A green piano! Can I play with it?" Her mom said, "Yes, you can play with it, but be careful."

Lily played with the green piano and made nice music. Other kids came to look and listen. They clapped their hands and danced to the music. Lily was very happy.

Then, a little boy named Tim joined Lily. He said, "Can I play the green piano too?" Lily said, "Yes, let's play together!" They played the green piano and made even more nice music.

In the end, all the kids in the park had fun playing with the green piano. They loved the music it made and they all had a great day.
<|end|>


