Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved popcorn. One sunny day, she asked her mom, "Can we make popcorn, please?" Her mom said, "Yes, let's make perfect popcorn together!"

Lily and her mom went to the kitchen. They put the popcorn in a big pot. Lily's mom said, "We need to prevent the popcorn from burning. So, we will shake the pot to keep it moving." Lily nodded and helped her mom shake the pot.

Soon, the popcorn started to pop! Pop, pop, pop! Lily and her mom laughed and smiled as they listened to the sounds. When the popcorn was ready, they poured it into a big bowl. They sat down to eat their perfect popcorn and enjoyed a fun day together.
<|end|>


