Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Tim. Tim had a big box with a lock on it. Inside the box, there was a secret toy. Tim wanted to play with the toy, but he could not unlock the box.

One day, Tim met a wise old cat. The cat said, "I know how to unlock the box. You need the key with a crack in it." Tim asked, "Where can I find the key?" The cat said, "Look under your bed."

Tim went home and looked under his bed. He found the key with a crack in it! He was so happy. He put the key in the lock and turned it. The lock clicked and the box opened. Tim was successful in unlocking the box.

Inside the box, there was a shiny toy car. Tim played with the car all day long. He thanked the wise old cat for helping him unlock the box. From that day on, Tim and the cat were the best of friends. And every time Tim looked at the crack in the key, he remembered how he became successful in opening the box.
<|end|>


