One day, a polite cat named Sam went for a walk. He saw a cable on the ground. Sam thought, "I want to play with the cable!" So he sat down and started to play.

A little girl named Sue saw Sam playing with the cable. She walked over to him and said, "Hi, cat! Can I play with the cable too?" Sam looked at Sue and nodded his head. They both sat down and played with the cable together.

After a while, Sue's mom called her to go home. Sue said, "Bye, cat! I had fun playing with you and the cable." Sam meowed and waved his paw. They both went their own way, but they knew they had made a new friend.
<|end|>


