One day, a cat and a dog were playing in the park. The cat was smooth and soft. The dog was big and brown. They liked to watch the birds fly in the sky.

The cat said to the dog, "I know a joke. Do you want to hear it?" The dog wagged his tail and said, "Yes, please tell me the joke!"

The cat smiled and said, "Why did the bird go to school? To learn how to fly!" The dog laughed and said, "That is a funny joke!"

They continued to play and watch the birds. They were happy and had lots of fun. The cat and dog were the best of friends.
<|end|>


