Once upon a time, there was a popular zoo. In the zoo, there were many animals like lions, monkeys, and elephants. Many kids loved to visit the zoo and see the animals.

One day, a little girl named Amy went to the zoo with her mom. They saw the big lion and Amy said, "Wow! Look at the big lion, Mom!" Her mom replied, "Yes, Amy. The lion is very big and strong."

As they walked, they saw the funny monkeys. The monkeys were jumping and playing. Amy and her mom paused to watch them. "I like the monkeys, Mom," said Amy. "They are so funny and make me laugh."

Next, they saw the big elephants. The elephants were eating and swinging their long trunks. Amy and her mom enjoyed watching them too. They had a great day at the popular zoo.
<|end|>


