Once upon a time, in a cool green park, there lived a little cat named Tom. Tom loved to play and run around the park. One day, Tom saw a big tree and wanted to climb it.

Tom started to step on the tree slowly. As he climbed higher, he saw a bird on a branch. "Hello, bird!" Tom said. "Do you want to play with me?" The bird looked at Tom and said, "No, thank you. I am going to take a nap." Tom felt sad but kept climbing the tree.

At the top of the tree, Tom found a nice spot to rest. He decided to take a nap too. As Tom slept, the cool wind blew gently. When Tom woke up, he saw the bird flying down to play with him. They played all day long and became good friends.
<|end|>


