Lily and Ben were best friends. They liked to play together in the park. One day, they found a big box under a tree. It had a sign that said "Do not open".

"What is in the box?" Lily asked.

"I don't know. Maybe it is a secret," Ben said.

"Can we open it?" Lily asked.

Ben looked around. He did not see anyone. He said, "OK, but we have to be quiet. We do not want anyone to see us."

They opened the box. Inside, they saw many toys. There were dolls, cars, balls, books, and more. They were very happy.

"Wow, look at all these toys!" Lily said.

"Let's choose one each. We can keep them as our secret," Ben said.

Lily chose a doll with a pink dress. She liked dolls. Ben chose a car with a red light. He liked cars.

They closed the box and hid it under the tree. They ran to the swings with their new toys. They played and laughed. They did not tell anyone about the box. It was their secret.
<|end|>


