Lily and Ben were friends. They liked to play in the park. They enjoyed the sun, the grass and the flowers. They also liked to listen to the birds. The birds sang in their ears. It was peaceful.

One day, a big dog came to the park. The dog was not nice. It barked and ran after Lily and Ben. Lily and Ben were scared. They tried to run away, but the dog was faster. The dog caught Ben and bit his ear. Ben cried and bled. Lily screamed and ran to help him.

A man saw what happened. He ran to the dog and kicked it. The dog let go of Ben and ran away. The man called for help. He took Ben and Lily to the hospital. Ben had to get stitches in his ear. Lily had to get a hug. They were both very sad. They did not enjoy the park anymore.
