"Guess what, Teddy? I have an invitation to Lily's birthday party. It is on Saturday. There will be cake and balloons and games. Do you want to come with me, Teddy? You can be my friend. We can have fun together."

Teddy did not answer. He was a lazy teddy bear. He only nodded his head. Sara smiled. She hugged her teddy bear. She was very happy. She whispered to her teddy bear.

"I love you, Teddy. You are the best teddy bear in the world."
