Sara and Ben are friends. They like to play in the park. Sara has a new dress. It is pink and has flowers. She is happy.

"Look at my dress, Ben!" Sara says. "Do you like it?"

"Yes, it is very pretty," Ben says. "Can we go to the fountain?"

"OK, let's go!" Sara says. They run to the fountain. It is big and has water. The water goes up and down. It is fun.

Sara and Ben play near the fountain. They throw stones and sticks in the water. They make splashes. They laugh.

