Tim and Jen were playing with their toy cars in the park. They liked to make noises and pretend they were racing. But then a big boy came and took Jen's car. He said it was his now and ran away. Jen was sad and angry. She wanted her car back.

Tim had an idea. He saw a big truck near the fence. It had a long thing on the back. Tim thought it looked like a missile. He told Jen to follow him. They ran to the truck and climbed on it. Tim found a button and pushed it. The missile flew off the truck and made a loud boom.

The big boy heard the boom and saw the smoke. He was scared and dropped Jen's car. He ran away too. Tim and Jen got the car back and smiled. They were happy and proud. They did not know that the missile was smelly. It was full of garbage and made a big mess. The truck driver was angry and shouted. He wanted his missile back. But Tim and Jen did not hear him. They ran back to the park and played with their toy cars. They did not steal anything again.
<|end|>


