Once upon a time, there was a big bird who loved to fly high in the sky. One day, the bird wanted to soar even higher than before. It flapped its mighty wings and flew up into the clouds.

But then, the bird saw something shiny on the ground. It was a bottle of oil. The bird thought it would be fun to play with the oil, so it swooped down to pick it up.

But as the bird landed on the ground, its feet slipped on the oily surface. The bird tried to fly away, but it couldn't get off the ground. It was stuck in the oil.

The bird cried out for help, but nobody came. And so, the poor bird was trapped in the oil forever. The end.
<|end|>


