Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Timmy. Timmy loved playing with his toy robots, especially his favorite one named Robby. One day, Timmy brought Robby to the park to play with his friends.

While they were playing, they heard a loud scream coming from the other side of the park. Timmy and his friends got frightened and didn't know what to do. Suddenly, they saw a robot walking towards them. Timmy was scared at first, but then he realized it was just a friendly robot.

The robot said, "Hello there! I heard someone scream. Are you okay?" Timmy and his friends told the robot they were scared, but they were okay now. The robot then said, "Don't be afraid. I am here to help." Timmy and his friends felt much better knowing the robot was there to protect them. From that day on, Timmy always brought Robby and his other toy robots to the park to play with the friendly robot.
<|end|>


