Out of the trees, a big black bear appeared. He had long sharp claws and big pointy teeth. All the animals were scared! But much to their surprise, the bear looked friendly. He was just happy to see all the animals out playing on the morning. The bear smiled and waved at everyone. 

The animals slowly gained courage and started to walk closer to the bear. Soon, they were all playing together, having a deep and wonderful time on the morning.
