Jimmy was so excited and hopped inside the helicopter. The driver pointed up in the sky and said, "Now, let's fly this important helicopter to the moon."

So off they went! Up, up, up into the sky. Jimmy soon forgot about being scared and just enjoyed the ride. After a few minutes, they were flying over the moon. Jimmy was so amazed and could not believe it. He waved to the moon and said goodbye. 

The next day, the helicopter driver came back and took Jimmy out to fly again. This time they flew to the sun! Jimmy was having so much fun that he said he wanted to fly in the important helicopter every day. 

