The little girl decides to be brave and walk outside her house. The monster is still following her wherever she goes. She is very uncomfortable with the monsterâ€˜s presence but decides to stay brave. 

The little girl walks to the playground and finds a group of her friends. They join her and the monster starts to shrink until it is only the size of her hand. Everyone cheers and the monster turns into a friendly fly. The little girl is surprised and happy she stayed brave. 

