Fred the frog hopped through the grass. He was so happy to be outside. The sun was bright and the birds were singing. Fred hopped and hopped until he heard a loud noise.

Fred looked up and saw a big truck. It zoomed by, making a loud noise. He was scared! 

But then he saw something that made him happy. In a nearby field, there were big, green bunnies hopping in the grass. Fred hopped over to the bunnies. They were so soft and gentle. 

Fred played with the bunnies all day, hopping and jumping around. They laughed and played together. Eventually, the sun went down and it was time for Fred to go home. He hopped away, thinking about how fun it was to play in the grass with the loud bunnies.
<|end|>


