Once upon a time, there was a dead armchair in the corner of the room. One day, it began to ring! The little boy was very surprised. He couldn't understand why the armchair was ringing. He started to jump up and down and laugh. The ringing became louder and louder. Suddenly, the ringing stopped and a funny voice came from the armchair. It said, "Boo! Did I scare you?". The little boy was so shocked! Then he saw a little mouse peeking out from the armchair's cushion. The little mouse was the one who had been ringing the armchair! The boy started to laugh and they both played together until it was time to go home.
<|end|>


