One day, Mommy had a very important job to do. She got out the mop and filled it with water.

Next, she took the mop and began to clean the kitchen. She moved it back and forth across the floor, and soon the kitchen was looking shiny and clean.

Mommy was tired after all that work. She decided that it was time for lunch. She opened up the fridge and recognized the tasty food inside.

Mommy took out the food and started to feed her little boy. He was so excited and ready to eat it all. Mommy smiled as she watched her son enjoy his lunch.

Once they were all finished eating, Mommy put away the scraps. She gave her son a hug and thanked him for being so helpful. She was so proud of him!

And with that, Mommy went back to the kitchen to get the mop and finish her job. She knew the floor would be very shiny and ready for her little boy to enjoy.
<|end|>


