Once upon a time, there was a broken owl in a tree. It was too high for the owl to get down by itself and it was stuck.

But then, one day, a little girl saw the owl. She knew that it needed to be rescued. So she got a ladder and she climbed up to the tree.

The girl carefully reached out and picked up the broken owl. She held on tightly and she helped it all the way down the ladder.

The girl stroked the owl's feathers and made sure it was safe. She was so happy that she was able to rescue the broken owl.
<|end|>


