Once upon a time there was a little girl called Kate. She was very excited because it was her third birthday. She had a big present waiting for her in the living room.

Kate was very anxious to open her present. She ran towards it and started to unwrap the paper. Inside was a big box. Inside the box was a brand new pencil sharpener.

Kate was delighted. She could use the sharpener to sharpen her pencils so that she could draw and colour.

It was the best birthday present ever. Kate hugged the pencil sharpener tight and was so happy that she almost forgot to have cake!
