One day a little girl called Molly was feeling very anxious. She was scared because she was going on an adventure. Her mum and dad said they would permit her to go, but she was very worried.

So they gave her a special shield to protect her. It was round and red, and very strong. Molly felt much better with her shield. She liked the way it made her feel safe.

Molly went on her adventure. She saw lots of different things and she made lots of new friends. She was no longer feeling anxious. 

The shield had permitted Molly to explore and have an amazing time. She thanked her mum and dad for giving her the shield. Molly had the most wonderful adventure and she never forgot the shield that had helped her to feel so brave.
