Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Sarah. She was three years old and loved exploring. 

One day, Sarah decided to explore the big, green garden outside her house. She ran around, looking at the pretty flowers and admiring the birds in the trees.

Suddenly, Sarah heard a noise! It was coming from a nearby bush. She nervously crept closer and saw a fluffy kitten! "Oh wow," Sarah exclaimed. She wanted to pick up the kitten, so she started to hurry towards it. 

Just then, Sarah heard her mum calling from inside the house. "Dinner is ready, Sarah! Come inside quickly!"

Sarah was so excited because she knew there was delicious steak on the table. She hurried into the house and was amazed by what she saw. There was an incredible steak and all her favourite vegetables. The smell was so yummy, Sarah couldn't wait to eat it all up!
