Once upon a time there were two friends, Jack and Jill. They shared a special secret, to find a magical shore. One day they decided to go on a journey to find it.

Jack and Jill walked and walked, until they reached the beach. When they looked to the horizon, they saw a beautiful shore in the distance. The sun was shining and the water was glistening, so they ran and ran until they reached the shore.

When they arrived, they noticed something strange. There was a big and shiny castle made of fake gold. Jack and Jill thought it was too good to be true, so they decided to share their secret and not tell anyone about the castle.

They ran back to the beach and decided to keep the magical shore just for themselves. But everytime they went there, they were filled with happiness and joy. They felt lucky to have found it, and had a lot of fun playing together at the magical shore.
