One day, a small boy went to the park. He saw a beautiful swan swimming in the lake. He wanted to take it home so he climbed into the lake and tried to take the swan. The boy was very humble and he begged the swan to come with him.

The swan was kind and decided to take the boy home. The swan was very gentle with the boy and soon they were back at his house. The boy was very glad to have the swan and they became good friends.

Every day, the boy would take care of the swan. He would feed it and give it water. He would play with the swan in the garden. 

The boy and the swan were happy together and they lived peacefully in the small boy's house.
