Once upon a time, three friends went on an adventure. They had to bring their luggage with them. The luggage was big and bossy, so it told the friends what to do. They were surprised!

Then, the friends stopped at a secret garden. There were beautiful flowers and butterflies. They saw a big can of spray. It was bright and colourful.

The bossy luggage said, "Let's use this spray to make these flowers even more beautiful!" So, the friends used the spray to make the flowers sparkle. The butterflies loved it!

The friends finished their adventure and went home. They laughed and smiled; they had a wonderful time.
