Once there was a wise old man who lived in a small house with a big yard. One day, he went outside to the yard to do some work. Suddenly, the wind started to blow hard and it was very cold. The old man started to shiver!

He knew he had to find something to keep him warm. He quickly ran back inside his house and put on a nice warm sweater. He put on his boots and a coat, too. 

He went back outside and could still feel the wind. But the wise old man was prepared and he didn't shiver anymore! He finished his work in the yard and went back inside with a big smile.
