Once there was a loyal kitten who lived in a big house. The kitten loved to play and explore every corner of the house. One day, the kitten wanted to go outside and explore even more. She pushed the screen door open and went off on her adventure. 

As the loyal kitten ran, she found a garden full of tall trees and brilliant flowers. She hopped, skipped and jumped all around, enjoying the new sights and smells that came with being outside.

Suddenly, she heard a loud noise in the distance and was so scared that her fur stood on end. She pushed her way back to the house and saw that a big gust of wind had caused the screen door to slam shut. Knowing that she was now safe, she gave a sigh of relief and went about her day. 

The loyal kitten was so happy she had been able to explore, but even happier to be back safe and sound.
<|end|>


