Once upon a time, there lived a big, enormous elephant. Everywhere the elephant went, he would wink and make all of his friends laugh and smile. One day, the elephant noticed a big, shiny machine near his pond. He walked over to it and noticed it had a big button. He pushed the button and saw something very exciting. The machine had printed an enormous wink! He couldn't believe his eyes and started to laugh. The elephant showed the wink to all of his friends. They thought it was so funny and laughed along with the elephant. Everyone was so happy and enjoyed the enormous wink that was printed. The end!
