Now Harry wanted to lead his mom and dad around the house to show them the model. He took his dad's hand and his mom's hand, and proudly showed them the model from all angles. His mom and dad were so impressed with how he put it together. 

It was a much needed distraction and the family spent a lovely afternoon admiring Harry's charming model.
