Once upon a time there were two friends. One was called Joe and the other was called Jane. They were playing together near the beach.

Suddenly, Joe asked Jane if she wanted to dive in the water. She said yes and so they went to the beach. Jane looked at Joe, who was jumping up and down and clapping his hands.

He ran towards the water and jumped in. He was swimming and diving around. Jane watched him and it made her smile. She wanted to dive too!

Joe shouted to Jane to join him, so she ran towards the water. She held her breath and dived in. The water was so blue and warm and she felt so free like a bird.

They swam around for a minute and then it was time to go home. Joe and Jane waved goodbye and started their journey back.

Joe and Jane had a useful day. They learnt that the best way to have fun is to dive in and explore new places.
