Once upon a time there was a naughty musician. He liked to eat a lot of food. Every day, the musician would eat yummy snacks and delicious treats.

One day, he went to get some chocolate cake. He was so naughty that he ate too much and it made him sick. He was not happy.

He ran to the park and saw a big tree. He sat down and thought about what he had done. He knew he shouldn't have eaten so much chocolate cake.

Then he saw a bird eating a juicy worm. The musician smiled and decided to be a little more careful with his food. He vowed to eat just enough and not too much. 

From that day on, the musician was more careful with the food he ate. He was still naughty but he was careful not to eat too much. The end.
