Just then, he heard someone call his name. It was his dad. He had been looking for him all over. Billy felt so much better when he saw his dad. They hugged each other tightly.

His dad held his hand as they made their way home. It was such a lively journey home with singing and lots of laughs. When they got there, Billy was glad to be back. His parents hugged him and showered him with kisses.
