Once upon a time there was a little girl. She was very brave, and she wanted to explore. One day she decided to take a walk. 

She entered a dark room. All of a sudden a bright light turned on. The little girl was very surprised. She realized the light came from a bulb hanging from the ceiling. 

The bulb was very loud. It made a buzzing sound and the little girl was not sure if she liked it. She touched the bulb and it got even brighter. She was amazed! 

The little girl decided to explore the room and see what else she could find. She was very happy she was brave enough to enter. The end.
