Milly was a bird. She was big and strong and wanted to soar. One day, Milly decided to take a trip in a van. The van was carrying heavy things but Milly knew she could carry them too. 

Milly flew over the van, she lifted it up into the air. Milly was so powerful that she could take the van higher and higher. She took it to the top of a nearby mountain. 

The view was so beautiful and Milly loved it! She flapped her wings and started to soar. She flew around and around, never getting tired. Milly was so happy. 

After some time, she went back to the van. She slowly lowered it back down the mountain and she continued on her trip. Milly was so proud of herself that she could soar and take the heavy van so high up!
