He started to climb the mountain. He climbed higher and higher until he finally reached the peak. He looked around and saw the most beautiful view he had ever seen. He could see for miles and miles.
Suddenly, the raven heard a sound. He turned and saw a small child at the peak of the mountain. The child had a big smile on his face. The raven was filled with joy and flew down to meet the child. They played together all day, until the sun went down and the sky started to get dark. 
