One day, Jack asked his mum if he could have a laser. His mum said yes, so she gave Jack a shiny new laser. He was so excited to play with it.

Jack decided to go outside in the garden and play with his laser. The garden was big and green, and he raced around, pretending to shoot his laser like a superhero.

Jack ran and ran until he felt very tired. So he sat down on the grass and relaxed. He felt so happy and peaceful in the sun.

But after a few minutes Jack was starting to get bored. So he asked his mum if he could go inside and relax with his laser in his bedroom. His mum said yes, so he went off and relaxed, feeling very content.
<|end|>


