Once upon a time, there was a little girl who was very tired. She was walking through the forest when she began to shiver. The trees were so tall and the air was so cold that she couldn't help it.

So, she kept walking and soon she came to a big tree with bright red leaves. The tree looked so beautiful that she decided to take a rest. She lay down and snuggled up in the leaves.

The sun was setting and the night was getting colder and colder. The girl shivered and shivered until she had no more shivers left!

But then she heard soft singing coming from deep in the forest. She followed the singing and soon she came upon a pond. She sat there and watched the stars light up the sky and she felt warm, again.

The little girl smiled and went home, feeling much more happy and not so tired as before.
<|end|>


