The honest friend was brave enough to take the boat out to sea and sailed away. After a long, long journey, the honest friend reached a new land. Here, the honest friend shared the stories about the beautiful island and the brave and strong friends. Everyone was very happy to hear the stories. 

The honest friend went back to the island and brought some new friends to share the happiness with. Now the island was even more happy and full of joy. Everyone started sharing things with each other and everyone was very honest. 

It was a beautiful island, filled with friends and happiness, and one that they would share forever.
