His mom and dad spread the coffee all around the kitchen. James watched with wide eyes as they carefully spread it on the table. He even got to try a tiny bit! He was so excited! 

He asked his parents why coffee was so different and special. His parents said that it was a fragrant drink and it made grown ups feel healthy and happy.

