Everyone was excited and wanted to get in the rocket. They all flew up high in the air again and saw something nobody had ever seen before. It was the most beautiful sight ever.

At the end of the day, everyone came back down to the ground again. Although the rocket was weak, it had taken them on a wonderful adventure.
