Rose was so excited, she spoke the magic words and the door unlocked! She opened it and was surprised to see her best friend inside.

Unfortunately, her friend was hurt. Rose got a soft warm napkin and put it on her friend's hurt head. Then, she gave her a tight hug. Her friend felt better and they both laughed. 

They had such a great adventure that night!
