The ghost cautiously approached the strange house. Slowly the old man opened the door and asked the ghost to come inside. The ghost felt scared but something made it stay. The old man told the ghost he had a special mission for it. The mission was to supply food to those who were hungry and could not get it themselves.

The ghost was honoured and agreed to take on the task. It quickly returned to the lake and began to supply food to all of its animal friends. It quickly became known as the dependable ghost, always helping those in need. The ghost was proud to have been asked to help and remained dependable for years to come.
