One day, the bunny was trying to hop up a small hill. But it was very steep, and no matter how hard he tried, he couldn't make it up. 

He was feeling sad, when suddenly, he heard a voice. The voice said, "Wait, bunny! I will help you up." The bunny looked around and saw little fairy coming down from the sky. 

The fairy waved her wand and released a soft light that helped the bunny to slowly move up the hill. Soon, the bunny was at the top of the hill. He was so happy and he thanked the fairy for helping him. 

The bunny and the fairy became good friends, and now they spend many happy days together hopping in the green meadow.
