Mary waited a few moments and tapped the oven gently. She opened it and when she saw the soup, it was steaming hot! She pretended to put it on the counter and served it to her pretend family. They all ate the pretend soup and said it was delicious!

Mary was having so much fun pretending to cook. She and her family ate pretend food all day. Mary was so happy and even learned a thing or two about cooking!
