Suddenly, she saw an ice-cream truck. Bella went to it and asked the driver for help. The driver told her that if she wanted milk, she would have to surrender and get in his truck. Bella was scared but she did it because she was very thirsty!

The driver gave her some yummy chocolate milk. Bella was so happy. She thanked the driver for the milk and for making her feel brave. Bella went home full and content. She learned that sometimes you have to surrender to get what you want. The end.
