When the clown left, Sarah felt something special. It was the feeling of spirit. She had laughed so much with the clown that it put a spell on her. No matter how sad she felt, she could still find joy in the world. Whenever she felt down, she could just remember the clown and his silly jokes, and it would make her laugh.
