Once upon a time, there was a little girl called May. She wanted to go outside and explore the world. So one day, she grabbed her bag and skipped outside. As she began to walk, she stumbled over a stone. But she was brave and kept going.

May reached a big building with tall towers in the distance. She was so excited to explore it! She walked up the steps and pressed a big red button on a modern machine next to the door. A loud stamp came from the machine. She had opened the door!

May went inside and walked around. She saw all sorts of interesting things, like a huge wooden desk, a shiny green chair and a bookshelf with lots of stories. She decided to take a nap on the green chair. But as she tried to sit down, she stumbled and fell onto the chair.

