Once upon a time there was a family. Mama, Daddy, and little Charlotte. Mama and Daddy wanted to make their home special and comfortable for Charlotte, so one weekend they decided to build a lamp. 

Mama and Daddy gathered the supplies. They got some wood, some paint and some sparkly stickers. They worked together to build the lamp and decided to paint it yellow and decorate it with the stickers. When they finished, the lamp looked very attractive. 

