Jack was very independent. He liked to do things on his own. But one day he was in the living room and suddenly he heard a loud bang. He started to panic and looked around to find what had caused the noise. He looked over and saw that a bookcase had fallen over. He started to cry and was too scared to touch it. He ran and hid in his bedroom but he was still scared. 

