Mia watched the video. It was bright, with lots of different colors. She liked it very much. Suddenly, she saw something move in the video. She felt excited and wanted to touch it. She reached out and pulled the thing from the video. She had never seen anything like it before. It was round, soft and colorful. Mia was so happy that she ran and showed it to her mom. Mom was surprised and smiled. She said, "Look Mia, you have pulled something different from the video!" Mia smiled and hugged the thing she had found. She was happy that she could take something so special from the video. She knew it was hers.
