Once upon a time, there was a small boy named Tom. Tom was very intelligent and was always curious about new things. One day, he came across a dark tunnel. He wanted to explore it, but he was scared to go in. He tried to go in, but he hated it! The tunnel seemed so dark and full of unknown things.

Tom's mom saw him trying to explore the tunnel and she got scared. She explained to Tom that the dark tunnel was dangerous and that he should not go in. But Tom was very curious! He wanted to know what was inside.

Tom's mom knew that he was very intelligent, so she suggested that they explore the tunnel together. She told him that she would be there with him to hold his hand and protect him.

Tom was very happy about this. He felt much better that his mom would be with him. Together, they explored the dark tunnel and found lots of interesting things. When it was time to go home, Tom was very excited about his adventure. He never wanted to hate the dark tunnel again.
