Once upon a time, there were two friends named Lucy and Jimmy. They liked to play together all the time. One day, they went to the park. It was very hot outside, so they decided to try to find some shade. 

Luckly, they found a nice tree with lots of leaves. They sat down in the shade and it was so comfortable. They spent all afternoon playing and laughing. 

Suddenly, Jimmy stopped and asked Lucy something. He wanted to understand why the shade was so comfortable. Lucy thought for a minute and said it was because the leaves of the tree blocked out the hot sun. When Jimmy understood what she said, they both smiled and jumped up. 

They ran around and had even more fun in the nice cool shade under the tree. The two friends were very happy and enjoyed the rest of their day at the park.
<|end|>


