Once upon a time, there was a girl named Sarah. She was three years old and loved to go outside and play. Today, Sarah wanted to go to the park.

She put on her coat and jumped into the car. When Sarah got to the park, she saw a lot of fun things she wanted to do. She saw slides, a big playground and even a pond. She was so excited!

At the pond, Sarah saw some ducks swimming. She wanted to go on the ice, too. But before she could get on, her mom said it was too slippery. Sarah was a little envious of the ducks.

But Sarah was happy to play on the playground and slide down the slides. She stayed at the park until it was dark. Then she got back in the car to go home. Sarah had had a great day at the park!
