Then the girl wanted to tie ribbons on all her toys. She practiced tying them as tight as she could but they all came undone.

So the girl asked her mom for help again. This time, her mom showed her how to double knot the ribbon. Now the girl was able to keep the ribbon tied! She was so proud of herself. 

The girl kept tying ribbons on things so she could make them look pretty and show everyone how good she was at tying.

The end.
