Once upon a time, there were two friends named Mary and Jody. Mary and Jody were best friends and loved to play together. 

One day Mary and Jody were playing in Mary's backyard. Mary mentioned to Jody that she wanted to go to a special place. Jody asked Mary where they were going and Mary said they were going to the earth! 

The girls began to dream about what the earth might be like. Jody mentioned that it would be full of purple flowers. Mary thought it might be covered in a bright purple sky.

The two friends got a little scared but still decided to go explore the earth. So, off they went! But when they arrived, what they saw was something quite unexpected. Everywhere they looked there were purple flowers, trees and even buildings covered in a bright purple color! 

Mary and Jody stayed to look around and eventually came home. They told everybody about their exciting adventure and all the wonderful purple things they had seen!
