Lily decided to show her coin to her friend, Timmy. As she was running to Timmy's house, she started to feel dizzy. When she arrived, she showed Timmy her coin and said, "Look, Timmy! My mommy and daddy gave me this shiny coin. I value it a lot!" 

Timmy looked at the coin and said, "Wow, that's so cool! I wish I had a shiny coin like that." Lily smiled and said, "Maybe your parents will give you one too!" 

After playing with Timmy for a while, Lily went back home. She showed her parents the coin again and said, "Thank you, mommy and daddy! I really value this coin." Her parents smiled and hugged her, feeling happy that Lily appreciated their gift.
