Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Timmy. Timmy loved to eat his dinner with a fork. One day, Timmy accidentally dropped his fork and it hurt his hand. His mom kissed his hand to make it feel better and said, "Don't worry, your hand will heal soon."

The next day, Timmy went outside to play with his friends. They found a harmless bug crawling on the ground. They picked it up and looked at it closely. Timmy's friend accidentally dropped the bug and it got hurt. Timmy said, "Let's help the bug heal!" They carefully put the bug back on the ground and watched it crawl away.

From that day on, Timmy was always careful with his fork and made sure to help any harmless creatures that he found.
