The next day, Lily's mommy took her to a farm. They saw many animals, but Lily was looking for the tall horse. Finally, they found it and Lily was so happy. She got to ride the horse and taste the fresh apples that the farmer gave them. Lily knew that she would never forget her adventure with the tall horse.
