Timmy's friend, Sally, noticed that Timmy was sad and asked him what was wrong. Timmy told Sally that he lost his colorful wallet. Sally said, "Don't worry, Timmy. Let's dance and maybe we'll find it!" So, Timmy and Sally danced around the park, hoping to find the wallet.

Suddenly, they saw a man walking towards them with Timmy's wallet in his hand. The man said, "Is this your wallet?" Timmy was so happy to have his wallet back and said, "Thank you so much!" Sally said, "See, dancing always helps!" Timmy and Sally continued to dance around the park, happy that they found the wallet.
