Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to play outside and explore the world around her. One day, while she was running around in the park, she tripped and fell. She hurt her shoulder and it made her cry.

Her mom came over and gave her a big hug. "It's okay, Lily," she said. "The pain will end soon." Lily wiped her tears and felt better knowing that the hurt would go away.

As they walked home, they saw a weird bird with colorful feathers. Lily pointed and said, "Look, Mommy! That bird looks funny!" Her mom smiled and said, "Yes, it does look weird, doesn't it?" They watched the bird for a little while before continuing on their way home.
