The little girl was so happy with the apple that she wanted to give something back to the tree. She made a loop out of a piece of string and put it on one of the branches. The tree was very grateful and felt even more wealthy now that it had a new decoration.

The moral of the story is that sharing makes us all feel wealthy in our hearts. Even if we split what we have, we can still be happy and make others happy too.
