Her mom replied, "Oh no! We can't have a dirty roof for the party. Let's clean it up." So, Lily and her mom got a ladder and some soap and water. They climbed up to the roof and scrubbed it clean. When they were finished, Lily said, "Wow, the roof looks so much better now!"

