Mommy smiled and said, "That's a great idea, Lily. But be careful not to slip on the drain."

Lily nodded and ran outside with her umbrella. She covered herself and danced in the rain, making sure to avoid the drain. When she came back inside, she was a little wet, but she had so much fun playing in the rain with her black umbrella.
