The grandson came over and they decided to build a big fort out of the lumber. They worked all day and finally finished the fort just as the sun began to set. The old lady was so happy and proud of what they had made.

But then, the sun got very hot and the fort started to melt! The old lady and her grandson were so surprised. They had never seen anything like it before. They quickly took apart the fort before it melted completely.

