Nemo swam closer to the shark, thinking it was his friend. But then, the shark opened its mouth and gobbled up Nemo in one big bite. Nemo's friends were sad and they all cried. They remembered how much fun they had with Nemo in the ocean.

And so, Nemo's friends learned a valuable lesson to always remember that some animals in the ocean can be dangerous, even if they seem harmless.
