Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She had a cute lamp in her room that she loved. One day, Lily's friend came to visit and accidentally broke the lamp. Lily was very sad and didn't know what to do.

Her mom told her that it's important to always take care of our things, but accidents happen. She also said that sometimes we have to return things that we borrow and be responsible for them.

Lily realized that she had borrowed her friend's toy and hadn't returned it yet. She decided to return it to her friend and apologize for the lamp. Her friend forgave her and they played together happily. Lily learned that it's important to be responsible and honest, and that true friends forgive and forget.
<|end|>


