Once upon a time, there was a small boy named Timmy. Timmy loved to play outside and explore. One day, he saw a big billboard with lots of colors and pictures. He asked his mom, "Mommy, what is that big sign?" His mom replied, "That's a billboard, Timmy. It's a sign that tells people about something they might like."

Timmy was curious and wanted to know more. He asked his mom, "Can we go see what it's about?" His mom said yes, so they set off to see the billboard. When they got closer, Timmy saw that it was an advertisement for a new toy. He was so excited and asked his mom if they could buy it. His mom said they would have to think about it and set a budget.

Timmy was happy just to have seen the billboard and learn something new. He went home and told his friends about it. They all wanted to see it too! The next day, they set off on an adventure to see the billboard together. They all had so much fun exploring and learning new things.
<|end|>


