Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She had a pretty bracelet that she loved to wear every day. One day, she went to the park to play with her friends. 

While playing, she noticed that her bracelet was missing. She looked everywhere but couldn't find it. She felt scared and sad. 

Her friend, Timmy, asked her what was wrong. Lily told him about her lost bracelet. Timmy asked if he could help her find it. They searched together and finally found the bracelet under a tree. Lily was so happy and thanked Timmy for his help. 

From that day on, Lily always made sure to keep her bracelet safe and secure. She never wanted to lose it again.
