Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She had a furry cat named Mittens. One day, Lily's friend Billy came over to play. Billy saw Mittens and said, "I wish I had a furry cat like Mittens." Lily said, "You can borrow Mittens if you want." Billy was happy and said, "Thank you, Lily. I will take good care of Mittens."

The next day, Billy came back to Lily's house with a present for Mittens. It was a toy mouse. Lily said, "That's so nice of you, Billy. Mittens will love it." Billy said, "I wanted to say thank you for lending me Mittens." Lily smiled and said, "You're welcome. I'm glad you and Mittens had fun."
