Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. One day, she saw a goose walking on the street. She said, "Hello, goose! Do you want to play with me?" The goose said, "Yes, I do!"

Lily and the goose played together all day long. They ran, jumped, and had so much fun! Lily said, "You act like a silly goose!" The goose laughed and said, "Thank you, Lily! You are so kind."

As the sun began to set, Lily said, "It's time for me to go home now." The goose looked sad and said, "I will miss you, Lily." Lily smiled and said, "Don't worry, we can play again tomorrow. The sky is so clear, it will be a beautiful day!" The goose smiled and said, "I can't wait!"
