Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She was very nervous about going to school. She didn't want to leave her mommy and daddy. But her mommy and daddy told her that she could trust her teacher to take care of her.

When Lily got to school, she felt scared. But then her teacher gave her a big hug and told her that everything would be okay. Lily felt much better after the hug. She started to play with her new friends and have fun.

At the end of the day, Lily was happy to see her mommy and daddy. She told them about her day and how her teacher helped her not be nervous anymore. Lily knew that she could trust her teacher and that made her feel safe.
