Tom and his mom saw a grill at the park. They wanted to cook some food. Tom's mom put some food on the grill. Tom watched and said, "Mom, I want to help you cook." His mom let him help a little bit.

When they were done cooking, Tom and his mom ate the food. It was very good. Tom said, "Mom, we complete the cooking. I had fun today." His mom smiled and said, "I had fun too, Tom. We should come to the park more often."
