Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Sue. She loved to bake yummy treats. One day, she baked a big cake for her friend Tom. Sue wanted to give the cake to Tom as a surprise.

Sue put the cake in a box and walked to Tom's house. On the way, she saw an empty mailbox. Sue thought, "I will put the cake in the mailbox, and Tom will find it when he checks his mail." So, Sue put the cake in the mailbox and went back home.

Later, Tom went to check his mail. He opened the mailbox and saw the cake. But, a big dog saw the cake too. The dog jumped up and took the cake from the mailbox. Tom said, "Oh no! My cake is gone!" The dog ran away with the cake, and Tom was very sad.
