Once upon a time, in a small house, there lived a little boy named Tim. Tim loved to watch films on his TV. His favorite film was about a big, hungry bear. One day, Tim's mom said they would have a party. Tim was very excited and wanted to help decorate for the party.

Tim thought about his favorite film and got an idea. He found some paper and drew the big, hungry bear from the film. He showed his mom and she smiled. She said, "That's a great idea, Tim! Let's put the bear on the wall for the party."

The day of the party came and all of Tim's friends came to the house. They saw the big, hungry bear on the wall and loved it! They played games and ate yummy food. At the end of the party, Tim's mom gave everyone a small toy bear to take home. All the kids were so happy and Tim felt proud that he helped decorate for the best party ever.
