Once upon a time, in a small house, there lived a little boy named Tim. Tim loved to eat tasty food. His mom always made tasty food for him. One day, she made a big plate of tasty food for Tim. But Tim did not want to eat it.

Tim's mom looked at him with a sad eye. She asked him, "Why do you refuse to eat the tasty food I made for you?" Tim said, "I want to go outside and play. I don't want to eat right now." Tim's mom said, "You must eat before you play."

Tim thought about it and did not want to make his mom sad. So, he ate the tasty food. His mom was very happy. After eating, Tim went outside to play with his friends. They all had a great time. And from that day on, Tim never refused to eat the tasty food his mom made for him.
<|end|>


