Pink said, "That's cool! Do you know about history?" Blue said, "No, what is history?" Pink said, "History is about things that happened a long time ago."

Blue and Pink talked about history and flew around together. Suddenly, a terrible storm came and Blue couldn't fly anymore. Pink tried to help but it was too late. Blue fell to the ground and didn't move anymore. Pink was sad and said, "I wish we could have soared together forever." The end.
