As Lily ate her spicy soup, she remembered the story her dad told her. She thought about how the boy prayed and won the race. Lily decided to pray too. She closed her eyes and asked for good luck.

The next day, Lily had a big test at school. She was nervous, but she remembered her prayer. She felt like she could win anything. And when she got her test back, she had gotten an A! Lily was so happy and thanked her parents for telling her the story about praying and winning.
