So Lily decided to show him how much fun it could be. She crawled into the box and invited Mr. Snuggles to join her. Soon, they were laughing and pretending they were on a pirate ship. Mr. Snuggles realized that playing in a box wasn't foolish at all - it was actually really fun! From that day on, Lily and her teddy bears had tea parties and pirate adventures in the box all the time.
