Once upon a time, a little boy named Timmy was playing outside. He saw a big, fluffy cloud in the sky. "Wow, that cloud is so pretty!" he said to himself. Suddenly, his friend Billy came over.

"Hey Timmy, let's play soccer!" said Billy.

"Okay!" Timmy replied. They started to kick the ball back and forth. But then, it started to get cold outside.

"Brrr, it's so cold!" said Timmy. "Let's go inside and have some hot chocolate."

"Good idea!" said Billy.

They went inside and Timmy's mom made them some hot chocolate. They sat by the window and watched the clouds go by. "Look at that cloud, it looks like a puppy!" said Timmy.

"Yeah, and that one looks like a dinosaur!" said Billy.

They drank their hot chocolate and talked about all the different shapes they saw in the clouds. It was a fun day playing outside with his friend and enjoying a warm drink on a cold day.
