Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Timmy. Timmy loved to eat pizza and spaghetti, but he was a messy eater. His mom always gave him a napkin to wipe his face, but he never used it. One day, Timmy went to a fancy restaurant with his family. He spilled his drink on the table and his mom gave him a napkin. Timmy didn't want to use it because it was cheap and scratchy. 

