Once upon a time, there was a big elephant. He was enormous! He liked to wear a red hat on his head. One day, he went to the store to buy a new hat. He found a green hat that fit his head perfectly. He was so happy! But when he tried to put the hat on, he realized that it was too small for his waist. He was sad because he couldn't wear his new hat. So, he went back to the store and found a bigger hat that fit his waist and head. Now he could wear his new hat and be happy again. The end.
