Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to watch the birds flying in the sky. One day, while she was looking up, she saw a big, fluffy cloud that looked like a bunny. Lily was very curious and wondered how the cloud could look like a bunny.

The next day, Lily went to the park to play. She saw a group of kids playing a game. One of the kids was being mean to the others and judging them for not playing well. Lily didn't like that and decided to play with the other kids. They had a lot of fun together.

As Lily was leaving the park, she saw the same big, fluffy cloud that looked like a bunny. She remembered how curious she was about it and realized that sometimes things can be different than they seem. Just like the cloud that looked like a bunny, people can also be different than they seem. She felt happy that she made new friends at the park and didn't judge them for not playing well.
<|end|>


