Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily who loved to climb. She climbed up trees, rocks, and even stairs. One day, she went to a big hall with her mommy. The hall was huge and had lots of stairs.

Lily's mommy said, "Be careful, Lily. The stairs are tight and steep. Don't climb them too fast."

