Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily who loved flowers. She would run through the garden, eager to pick the prettiest ones. One day, she found a big, red flower and picked it carefully. As she walked away, she heard a sound. It was a bird whistling! Lily was surprised and happy. She looked around and saw the bird sitting on a branch. She whistled back and the bird flew down to her. They became friends and played together in the garden every day. Lily was very happy to have a new friend who could whistle so beautifully.
