Anna and Ben are friends. They like to play outside. Today is a sunny day. They go to the park with their mom.

They see a big slide. They run to the slide. They take turns to go down. They have fun. They laugh and shout.

Then they see a big cloud. The cloud is gray and dark. It covers the sun. They feel cold. They hear thunder. They are scared.

They run to their mom. Their mom hugs them. She says, "Don't worry. It is just a storm. It will go away soon."

They look at the sky. They see a rainbow. The rainbow is bright and colorful. It appears after the rain. They smile. They say, "Wow! Look at the rainbow! It is so pretty!"

They forget the storm. They are happy. They want to play more. They are not lazy. They are brave. They love today.
<|end|>


