Tom and Lily were playing in the park. They saw a large bottle on the grass. It was shiny and blue. They ran to the bottle and picked it up.

"Wow, look at this bottle!" Tom said. "It is so big and pretty!"

"Can I have it?" Lily asked. "I like blue. It is my favorite color."

