Tom and Lily were twins who liked to play outside. One day, they went with their mom and dad to a big park. There was a lake in the park, and Tom and Lily wanted to see it.

"Look, Lily, look!" Tom said, pointing to the water. "The lake is so big and blue! Can we go near it?"

"OK, Tom, but be careful," Lily said. "The lake is deep and wet. We don't want to fall in."

They ran to the edge of the lake and saw many things. They saw fish and ducks and frogs. They saw boats and rocks and trees. They saw the sun and the sky and the clouds.

"Wow, this is so pretty!" Lily said, smiling. "Can we touch the water?"

"Sure, Lily, but only a little bit," Tom said. "The water is cold and splashy. We don't want to get wet."

They dipped their fingers in the water and felt it. It was cold and splashy, just like Tom said. They laughed and made ripples and bubbles.

"Look, Tom, look!" Lily said, pointing to the other side of the lake. "There is a big hill over there! It is so high and green! Can we go there?"

"OK, Lily, but be careful," Tom said. "The hill is steep and hard. We don't want to get hurt."

They ran to the other side of the lake and saw the hill. It was high and green, just like Lily said. It was also mighty and strong. It made Tom and Lily feel small and brave.

"Wow, this is so cool!" Tom said, excited. "Can we climb the hill?"

"Sure, Tom, but only a little bit," Lily said. "The hill is rough and rocky. We don't want to fall down."

They climbed the hill and felt it. It was rough and rocky, just like Lily said. They had to use their hands and feet and be careful. They reached the top and saw the whole park.

"Look, Lily, look!" Tom said, amazed. "We can see everything from here! The lake, the boats, the trees, the sun, the sky, the clouds! We are so high!"

"Wow, this is so amazing!" Lily said, happy. "We did it, Tom! We climbed the hill! We are so mighty!"

They hugged and cheered and felt proud. They looked at the lake and the hill and felt happy. They had a lot of fun at the park. They loved to play outside.
<|end|>


