Mommy and Lily called Coco and asked him to come down. Coco was afraid of the dog, but he saw Lily and Mommy and trusted them. He flew down and landed on Lily's shoulder. Lily hugged Coco and said, "I'm sorry, Coco, I'm glad you are safe. I love you." Coco hugged Lily and said, "I love you too." Mommy smiled and said, "Let's go home, Lily and Coco. You are both brave and good." Lily and Coco nodded and went home with Mommy. They were happy and safe.
