Mom was very compassionate. She loved Anna and Ben and answered their questions. She also hugged them and gave them snacks. She said, "You are both very smart and curious. I am proud of you!"

Anna and Ben smiled. They were happy and grateful. They said, "We love you, mom!" They hugged mom and looked at the sky. They wondered what else they could learn.
