When they arrived, a kind nurse welcomed them. She said everyone was so glad they came and they were going to make sure Emily felt better.

The doctor gave Emily a check-up. She looked into Emily's ears, nose and throat. The doctor said Emily was going to have to rest and take her medicine so she would get better.

