Once, in the winter, there was a flower that lived in a garden. It was cold and uncomfortable in the winter and the flower felt sad. But everyday, the sun shone and the flower started to bloom. The flower opened up its petals and started to feel happy and warm. The petals shone in the winter sun and the flower felt so peaceful. As time went on, the flower kept growing and blooming until the winter ended. Finally it was summer and the garden was full of flowers, blooming and growing. The winter was gone and it was time for the flower to be happy.
