After taking the medicine, the doctor said the boy should go to the ocean. He said to play in the waves and splash in the water. He said it would make him feel better.

So, the boy and his mommy and daddy went to the beach. He splashed and played in the waves. The water felt so good and he felt so safe. 

The boy got better and lived happily ever after. Whenever he felt sick, he would go to the beach and splash in the waves. It made him feel much better.
