Once there was a green peach that lived on a tree. The peach was very happy, until one day a strong wind blew. The wind shook the tree, and the peach was scared.

The peach fell from the tree and landed on the grass. The peach felt alone, but then she met a bee. The bee said, "Don't be scared. I'll keep you safe!"

The bee and the peach started to play together. They rolled around on the grass and laughed. They shook together and had so much fun.

The bee said goodbye and flew away. The peach was sad, but he was also very happy he made a new friend!
