Once upon a time there was a little girl. She was called Daisy. Daisy was very brave.

One day she was walking in the woods when she saw someone in trouble. It was a little bird. The bird had gotten stuck in a big mud puddle.

Daisy was determined to rescue the bird. She ran to the nearest house and asked for help.

The lady at the house gave Daisy some powder. Daisy carefully sprinkled the powder around the bird and the mud started to dry up.

Daisy kept sprinkling until the bird was free. The bird was very happy and thanked Daisy. 

Daisy was very happy too. She was so persistent and had rescued the little bird.
<|end|>


