The cat jumped from the tree, and landed in a soft pile of leaves. Suddenly, the cat felt happy and proud!
After that, the cat tried all kinds of new things, and believed in its own success. Every time it did something, it felt stronger and more confident. 
Eventually, the fat cat learned that if you believe in yourself and try your best, success will follow!
