Once upon a time there was a restless goose. He wanted to go on a big adventure but his mom said no. So the goose decided to resist and flew away. 

The goose flew though the sky looking for a fun place to explore. Far away in a distant land, he found a magical forest. The goose was so excited to go in and explore. He flew into the forest and saw so many amazing things!

He saw butterflies, and bees, and cute little bunnies. He also saw a big red apple tree. The goose was thrilled! He started to eat the apples and play with the animals. 

The day went quickly, and soon it was getting dark. The goose knew it was time to fly home. But he was having too much fun so he decided to resist and spend one more night in the magical forest. 

The next day the goose met some new friends, and together they explored the forest. When it was time to go home, the goose was sad but excited for the next adventure. He waved goodbye to his new friends and flew back home to his mom.
<|end|>


