Once upon a time, there was a tall mouse who lived deep in the woods. He was always looking for food to eat and fun things to do. One day he decided to make a trap. He wanted to catch his own food!

He found some sticks, some string, and a big box. He worked hard to put it all together. Then he put a piece of cheese inside the box to attract the animals.

Soon, he saw a big rabbit near the trap. The rabbit was sniffing the cheese. Then all of a sudden, the trap closed and the rabbit was caught!

The tall mouse was so happy. He finally owned his own trap and caught his own food! He picked up the rabbit and went for a run in the woods. He now had a lot of delicious food for himself. The end.
