From behind the bush, the bow could see a park. He had never seen so much green before! He carefully stepped out from behind the bush and ran towards the park. 

When he got to the park, the bow was amazed. He saw big trees, colorful flowers, and children running around and playing. He was so happy. The bow played in the park all day and finally felt content. 

