The owner asked the people to come back in a few days when the renovations were done. Everyone could not wait to get back to shopping in the mall. 

The owner worked very hard and soon the mall was ready to open again. Everyone was so happy when they saw that the mall was successful again. Everyone kept shopping and having fun everyday.

