Once upon a time, there was an envelope. It was very fragile. One day, a person came and put the envelope in a box and locked it.

The person then clicked their fingers and a big giant appeared. "Take the box and put it in the castle," said the person. The giant nodded and carried the box away.

When the giant reached the castle, he opened the door and put the box inside. Then he put the key in the keyhole, clicked it twice and locked the door.

Now the envelope was safe and sound. No one could open the door until the person came back with the special key. 

The End.
<|end|>


