Once there was a zebra. He was so careful in all that he did. Everywhere he went, he looked around carefully and paid attention to the details.

One day he went to a new place. He wanted to be extra careful and make sure he didn't get lost. As he looked around, he saw something interesting - a big pond. He watched as the sun shone on the water.

He walked up to the pond, getting closer and closer. He was so curious. When he was finally close enough, he saw some fish swimming in the water. That's when he saw the most beautiful thing of all - a zebra!

It was a zebra, just like him. He wanted to get a closer look, so he walked up to the edge of the pond. But he was so careless and in his excitement, he slipped and fell into the water!

He was so scared and almost started to cry. But then, the other zebra came over to him and helped him get out of the pond. The two zebras stayed together for a long time, enjoying the beautiful day.
