Once upon a time, there was a very glad girl. She had a special hoop. Every day, she would take her hoop outside in her yard to play. She would keep throwing the hoop as far as she could, then she would chase it and throw it again. The girl kept playing with her hoop, she was so glad that it never seemed to get boring.

