The girl walked far and wide all around the neighbourhood, looking for her hoop. Finally, she reached a park. As she passed by a slide, she spotted her hoop on the grass nearby. She was so glad to see it again.

The girl picked up her hoop and ran back home. After that, she always kept the hoop near her so she wouldn't lose it again. Every day, she would take it back outside and play with it. She was so glad she'd found her hoop, and she kept playing with it forever.
