Suddenly, he heard a voice. It said: "Hey, lion! I'm scared of you. Is there anything I can do to make you leave?" 

The lion was so surprised that he didn't say anything. But then he saw a pill lying on the floor.

The lion told the voice that if he ate the pill, it would make him as strong and mighty as any other animal. The voice agreed and the lion ate it.

The lion felt a new power inside him! He was so mighty and brave that the elephant and all the other animals stopped teasing him. The lion lived happily ever after and was never bothered again.
