Mummy said they should shoot the strawberries with their slingshot. Sammy thought this sounded like a lot of fun so he grabbed his slingshot and Mummy grabbed hers too. They had a race to see who could shoot the most strawberries. 

Sammy was very excited and he shot at lots of strawberries. He was so proud when he got a big one. Mummy was very proud of her little boy too and gave him a big hug. 

By the end of the game, Sammy and Mummy had shot so many strawberries that their backyard was full of yummy treats. They took all of the strawberries inside and made a delicious strawberry pie. Yum!
