She wanted to get a closer look, so she carefully stepped into the water. When she got close enough, the wave lifted her up and started to carry her away!

The girl closed her eyes and started to laugh, feeling the wave's power and warmth. She had never been so happy. She thanked the wave and said goodbye, then watched it disappear into the sea. 

When the wave was gone, the girl knew she had found something special. She was amazed at all of the interesting, creative things nature had to offer!
