The metal box was so happy it began to move around. It asked the little girl to put coins inside its metal body. She put one coin at a time and soon the box was full.

The metal box looked very happy. It said, "Thank you for playing with me. I'm so happy because now I have lots of coins!" 

The little girl smiled and told the metal box, "You're welcome. I had lots of fun playing with you." 

