After a while, he found a tiny dragon. The dragon was scared and alone. It needed help! The brave knight was always ready to help those who needed it, so he spent the rest of the day hunting for food and building a warm den for the dragon.

The knight was very happy when he saw the dragon settled in its new home. He smiled and said goodbye to the dragon, before riding off on his horse. He will always be ready to protect and help those who are in need.
