Once upon a time there was a nosy oat named Joe. Every day Joe would go on a new adventure. One day he decided to go on a journey to the beach. He asked his friends to join him, but they said no.

On the way to the beach, Joe saw a pond with lots of animals. He was so nosy he wanted to explore what was in the pond. He hopped in and splashed around, until he found a big fish. Joe said hello to the fish, but it wouldn't talk back. So Joe kept swimming around.

At the beach, Joe found a big boat. He was so nosy that he wanted to go for a sail. He climbed into the boat, and found an old oat. It looked like the perfect snack, so Joe ate the oat. 

The boat sailed away and Joe laughed and waved goodbye to the beach. Joe had such a wonderful adventure, and he was happy to find the yummy oat. He decided to go home and tell his friends all about it.
