The person then saw a figure in the distance. As it got closer, the person could see that it was a small child! When the child got close, the person realized that it was a 3 year old toddler. The person took a deep breath, and the panic started to go away. 

The toddler came over and smiled at the person. The toddler's smile was so sweet that the person couldn't help but smile back. The person then knelt down and hugged the toddler. After that, the person and the toddler played tag and had a great time! From then on, whenever the person was feeling scared, they just thought of the toddler's sweet smile, and then they didn't panic anymore.
