One day, a brown dog named Max went to the park. It was very hot, so Max wanted to find a way to make it cooler. He saw a big tree with lots of shade. Max ran to the tree and lay down in the shade. Now, he felt cooler and happier.

Max saw a little girl named Lily. She was also feeling hot. Max went to Lily and said, "Come with me. I know how to make you cooler." Lily smiled and followed Max to the big tree. They both sat under the tree and felt the cool shade.

Lily said, "Thank you, Max! You made me cooler and now I am happy." Max wagged his tail and felt proud. They both played under the tree all day, feeling cooler and having fun together.
