One day, Timmy went to the doctor's office to get weighed. The doctor put him on a scale and told him he was a little too heavy. Timmy didn't understand what that meant, but he knew it didn't sound good.

Later that day, Timmy's mom made him a healthy dinner and they talked about how important it is to take care of your body. Timmy listened carefully and promised to eat more fruits and vegetables.

From that day on, Timmy worked hard to eat healthy and exercise more. He didn't want to suffer from being overweight. And as he grew up, he continued to be creative and draw beautiful pictures that he shared with the world.
