At the park, Lily saw a big slide that she wanted to go on. But her mom said she had to wait until after lunch. So, Lily sat down on the grass and ate her sandwich. After lunch, Lily ran to the slide and climbed up the ladder. When she got to the top, she realized her waist was too small for the slide! 

Lily's mom helped her go down the slide safely and they went to play on the swings instead. Lily hugged her teddy bear and felt happy. She decided that she had a great day at the park. The end.
