Once upon a time, there was a big red octopus that lived in the ocean. The octopus had eight long arms and loved to swim around. One day, a little fish swam by and the octopus wanted to play. But when the octopus tried to grab the fish, it accidentally pinched it with one of its arms. The fish swam away quickly and the octopus felt sad. 

The next day, the octopus saw the fish again and apologized for pinching it. The fish forgave the octopus and they became friends. They played together all day and had so much fun. From that day on, the octopus was careful not to pinch its friends and they all lived happily in the ocean.
<|end|>


