<|asst|>
Once upon a time, a little mole named Molly wandered around the forest. She was looking for some yummy worms to eat for breakfast. Suddenly, she heard a loud noise and got scared. She quickly dug a hole to hide in.

As she was hiding, she heard a voice say, "Hello there, little mole. What are you doing here?"

Molly peeked out of her hole and saw a kind rabbit looking at her. She said, "I'm just looking for some breakfast. I'm a little spoiled and like my food just right."

The rabbit laughed and said, "I know what you mean. I'm the same way. Let me help you find some yummy worms."

Together, they wandered through the forest and found the best worms Molly had ever tasted. She thanked the rabbit and they became good friends. From that day on, Molly never wandered alone again.
<|end|>


