Once upon a time, there was a little bird named Tweety. Tweety was very happy because he had a lot of friends. One day, Tweety was flying to meet his friends when he saw a banana peel on the ground. He didn't see it and slipped on it! 

Tweety's heart was beating very fast because he was scared. Luckily, he didn't get hurt because he was very thin. Tweety learned a lesson that day, and he always looked where he was going after that.
