Lila and Ben are adventurous. They like to play with their ship in the pond. They pretend they are pirates and explorers. They have a map and a treasure chest.

One day, they see a big duck in the pond. The duck is swimming near their ship. Lila and Ben are curious. They want to be friends with the duck. They give the duck some bread. The duck likes the bread. It quacks and wags its tail.

The duck follows their ship. Lila and Ben are happy. They think the duck is their new crew. They show the duck their map and their treasure chest. The duck looks at them with its bright eyes. It quacks and wags its tail again.

Lila and Ben have a fun day with the duck. They sail around the pond and find new places. They share their bread and their treasure with the duck. They are adventurous and kind. The duck is their best friend. They name the duck Quack.
