Lily liked to help her mom mail letters. She would put them in the big blue box on the street. She would say, "Bye bye, letters! Have a good trip!"

One day, Lily saw a chubby man in a red suit and a big bag. He was putting things in the big blue box. Lily was curious. She asked, "What are you doing, mister?"

The man smiled and said, "I'm mailing presents for Christmas. I'm Santa Claus. Do you want a present, little girl?"

Lily nodded. She loved presents. She said, "Yes, please! I want a doll and a book and a hat and..."

Santa laughed and said, "Whoa, whoa, whoa! That's a lot of things. How about I give you one thing now, and the rest later?"

Lily agreed. She was happy to get anything. Santa reached into his bag and pulled out a pair of pants. They were pink and sparkly and had flowers on them. Lily loved them. She said, "Thank you, Santa! They are so pretty!"

Santa said, "You're welcome, Lily. I'm glad you like them. Now, you have to promise me something. You have to be good and listen to your mom and dad. And you have to wear these pants when you mail letters. They are magic pants. They will make your letters fly faster and reach their friends sooner. Can you do that?"

Lily nodded. She was excited to try the magic pants. She said, "I promise, Santa. I will be good and wear the pants. Thank you, thank you, thank you!"

Santa hugged her and said, "Merry Christmas, Lily. I'll see you soon." He waved and walked away with his bag.

Lily ran to her mom and showed her the pants. She said, "Look, mom! Santa gave me magic pants! They will help me mail letters!"

Her mom smiled and said, "Wow, Lily! That's amazing! You are a very lucky girl. Let's go home and try them on."

Lily and her mom went home. Lily put on the pants and felt very happy. She couldn't wait to mail more letters with her magic pants. She hoped Santa would like her letters too. She thought he was very nice and funny and chubby. She liked him a lot.
